  <h2>
    <span class="">在哪儿买这本书</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;

  </h2>


        <ul class="bs noline more-after ">
          
                
                <li class="">
                    <a target="_blank" href="https://book.douban.com/link2/?lowest=1110&amp;pre=0&amp;vendor=jingdong&amp;srcpage=subject&amp;price=1310&amp;pos=1&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Funion-click.jd.com%2Fjdc%3Fe%3D%26p%3DAyIOZR5aEQISA1AYUyUCEwZRHlwVCiJDCkMFSjJLQhBaUAscSkIBR0ROVw1VC0dFFQMTA1AcWx0dS0IJRmtyUG5aEHI8bWJWXxV%252BHxRlE1gjfAllDh43Uh5cEwUbBFIrWxEDFgNlK1sUMkBpja3tzaejG4Gx1MCKhTdUK1sQCxsDUBpdHQMVDlQrXCXbkrCDucnMnJjS3YxrJTIi%26t%3DW1dCFBBFC1pXUwkEAEAdQFkJBVsUAxYCUhtTCltXWwg%253D&amp;cntvendor=3&amp;srcsubj=2381658&amp;type=bkbuy&amp;subject=2381658" class="">
                      <span class="">京东商城</span>
